'''石灰石-石膏法'''是應用最廣泛的[[脫硫|脫硫]]方法，因為脫硫效率高且適應性強<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Nygaard |first1=Helle G. |last2=Kiil |first2=Søren |last3=Johnsson |first3=Jan E. |last4=Jensen |first4=Jørgen N. |last5=Hansen |first5=Jørn |last6=Fogh |first6=Folmer |last7=Dam-Johansen |first7=Kim |title=Full-scale measurements of SO2 gas phase concentrations and slurry compositions in a wet flue gas desulphurisation spray absorber |journal=Fuel |date=2004-06 |volume=83 |issue=9 |pages=1151–1164 |doi=10.1016/j.fuel.2003.12.007 |accessdate=2019-12-19}}</ref>而可以應用於[[煙道氣|煙道氣]]脫硫、[[汽車|汽車]]尾氣脫硫及[[工廠|工廠]]廢氣脫硫等。[[美國|美國]]、[[德國|德國]]及[[日本|日本]]有90%以上的[[火力發電廠|火力發電廠]]使用該方法脫硫。石灰石-石膏法的原理是採用噴淋塔[[結構|結構]]，含塵煙氣與霧化的脫硫漿液逆向接觸，通過漿液的洗滌作用，脫除煙氣中的顆粒物和有害[[物質|物質]]<ref>{{cite journal |author1=LI B |author2=WANG H L |author3=XU Y Y, et al. |title=Reduction of trace elements in flue gas by wet desulphurization facilities in coal-fired power plants |journal=Journal of China Coal Society |date=2015 |volume=40 |issue=10 |page=2479-83 |doi=10.13225/j.cnki.jccs.2015.0146 |accessdate=2019-12-19}}</ref>。然而，脫硫漿液霧化等的脫硫過程中可能會產生新的亞[[微米|微米]]級微粒，很容易就被煙氣夾帶出脫硫系統，令脫硫淨煙氣中的顆粒物[[濃度|濃度]]提升<ref>NIELSEN M T, LIVBJERG H, FOGH C L, 等.Formation and emission of fine particles from two coal-fired power plants. Combustion Science and Technology, 2002, 174(2): 79-113.</ref>。

該方法利用了以下反應： 

CaCO<sub><small>3</small></sub> + SO<sub><small>2</small></sub> =△= CaSO<sub><small>3</small></sub> + CO<sub><small>2</small></sub> 2CaSO<sub><small>3</small></sub> + O<sub><small>2</small></sub> == 2CaSO<sub><small>4</small></sub> 

